Like. really?

196
00:09:42.650 --> 00:09:44.553
You know we don't even like him.

197
00:09:46.120 --> 00:09:47.888
Just so annoying.

198
00:09:50.057 --> 00:09:51.625
Yeah.

199
00:09:53.994 --> 00:09:56.130
Honestly. 'cause that's what
